title: Oka Chair
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Chunky sculpted timber make up the Oka chairs wide spacious frame. Designed to showcase the best of what nature has to offer its simple wool upholstery reveals the hemp rope suspension underneath. Soft forms and ample seating invites multiple ways to sit and relax while bold details and clever joinery carries a presence into any space it is placed. 

